  "id": "RAW_f1c4755c",
  "title": "探元计划 NextGen 终审路演收官，两大赛道 12 家文化场景入围最终榜单",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTE0ODA2MQ==&mid=2650996413&idx=2&sn=fd67ca7d70453dbdf216b1bb63f11f51",
  "date": "2026-04-09 09:51:00",
  "author": "腾讯研究院",
  "siteName": "腾讯研究院",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dbabd0fc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fsm1UZBHjpbgM5YDQWjhKpdVLBXGT8GzFFj7wz8h1Zccmch5QnH7kDVe8LiaYpgm6YJAtbH58zGT5sL7ucVOt9CfPJPZSIR2tjkj6NSKuxT7Y%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">2026年3月17日至18日，由腾讯SSV与腾讯研究院共同发起的探元计划NextGen终审路演在北京“文化智境·石景山区人工智能大模型集聚区”圆满举办。本次终审路演聚焦“数智活化”与“AI考古”两大赛道，共计有12家文化场景入围最终</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">榜单。</span></span></strong></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">自2025年12月探元计划NextGen正式启动以来，这场以“探寻科技创新范式，元启文化数智焕活”为目标的科技与文化深度共创之旅，获得了社会各界的广泛关注与踊跃参与。在“数智活化”与“AI考古”两大核心赛道上，共收到了来自场景方单位、高校、科研院所</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">与科技企业的近150份高质量</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">申报方案，其中数智活化赛道申报需求近90项，AI考古赛道申报项目59项。经过多轮严谨评审，两大赛道共有22个项目脱颖而出，晋级终审路演。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;border-bottom: 9px solid rgba(143, 147, 206, 0.26);border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;\">\n     <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: -10px;\">\n      <div style=\"padding-left:13px;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:1.5;padding-right:13px;\">\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">公平公正，严谨评审：</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">两大赛道最终入围榜单公示</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为确保本次终审路演的权威性与专业性，评审组建了跨学科、高规格的专家评审团。评审团成员汇聚了来自中国科学院、中国社会科学院古代史研究所等国家级科研院所的权威学者，北京大学、山东大学等顶尖高校的学科专家，以及腾讯公司的专家代表。专家领域全面覆盖人工智能、数字人文、考古学、古文字学、美术史、文物保护、文化产业等关键方向，为两个赛道提供了精准、多维的学术与产业视角。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100015956\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a15d571f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FibJhwiav9msqa57ZMXy8rYRmXqIVqIbl9RQZW1BfT0mEE9UZRUb9JREn3JylcDkBuOARibaNujQSEcbSFMETcia4yvktwv0xqOSm65TRk17XjcE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D0\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">数智</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">活化赛道终审路</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">演专家合影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7490740740740741\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100015955\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dc232c5c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FibJhwiav9msqYO0myQKw7ibYicCK5gyGjTX3ExyQribibC6ibfuyNLDz5icwAF6OXakYDtJa5bPM5t7QYJVn64ITUrrMcHYBnjKaCDNibcL8WYYS2CibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AI考古赛道终审路演专家合影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">评审专家从“行业解法打磨”“技术创新培育”与“解决方案特点”三大维度对项目进行综合评议，充分关注项目的真实性、可行性、创新性、示范性与影响力，确保创新技术真正服务于文化场景的“真问题”、创造“真价值”。针对数智活化与AI考古两大赛道不同的属性与目标，评审团进行了极具针对性的专业评估：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">数智活化赛道评审聚焦项目破解行业主要难点、痛点、堵点问题的能力，运用AI、大数据等前沿技术，挖掘引领行业的创新解决方案，形成可复制推广的行业范式。同时入选项目评审强调“公益性”与“标杆性”，项目算法、工具、数据集等成果需向社会开放，促进社会参与，带动行业发展。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">AI考古赛道评审聚焦于人工智能技术在考古研究与文化遗产保护中的创新应用，关注项目是否能够通过科技赋能，破解传统考古工作中的关键难题，为中华文明探源和文化遗产保护提供新的技术路径。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">同时，评审专家对22个入围路演团队扎实的技术基础、清晰的落地规划以及所展现出的行业潜力给予了肯定。专家们认为，这些项目不仅精准反映了当前文化与科技深度融合的前沿探索，更激发了关于未来文化遗产保护、研究与活化的无限想象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3583959899749373\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"798\" style=\"height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 677px !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ibJhwiav9msqasYKAX0iaspa8pCBo6b3pxb4YScwWHFn7at7KcGqYYNbE9MAaRzRv4u4eAtlRKYJbMzNticBJJf52fzWG2rlGSolcaIibBWTxpUQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"214\" data-imgfileid=\"100015968\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=439fc8f0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJhwiav9msqasYKAX0iaspa8pCBo6b3pxb4YScwWHFn7at7KcGqYYNbE9MAaRzRv4u4eAtlRKYJbMzNticBJJf52fzWG2rlGSolcaIibBWTxpUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">数智活化赛道评审专家点评</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:16px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3893805309734513\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"904\" style=\"width: 677px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ibJhwiav9msqYKib8xWjub0seBTdQbEeJacSl9s83ApTCKtOicAuq5fpuS7DV9TJOLgpmnrT4qt4zdQlhLia6s2XSGJYewUdqSgFXDhhKRgn2OK4/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"264\" data-cropsely2=\"201\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"225\" data-imgfileid=\"100015967\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1f9b1a7c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJhwiav9msqYKib8xWjub0seBTdQbEeJacSl9s83ApTCKtOicAuq5fpuS7DV9TJOLgpmnrT4qt4zdQlhLia6s2XSGJYewUdqSgFXDhhKRgn2OK4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">AI考古赛道评审专家点评</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">经评审团独立、审慎的评分，严格遵循“公平、公正、客观、独立”的原则，保障评审团的权威性、专业性，确保评审过程的全面性和公正性，遴选出探元计划NextGen数智活化赛道与AI考古赛道的最终入围榜单。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;border-bottom: 9px solid rgba(143, 147, 206, 0.26);border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;\">\n     <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: -10px;\">\n      <div style=\"padding-left:13px;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:1.5;padding-right:13px;\">\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">探元计划NextGen数智活化赛道榜单</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">(排名不分先后)</span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9506346967559943\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1418\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"549\" data-imgfileid=\"503512749\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3c82e819&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fsm1UZBHjpbiaebIN6ZETsXmg2FUlLXXn3WUFyVfzwoFficRic5a2fWkaPDEzfFvDEh9g0vSE3rnICJRSj4UQuRvPeIibq5yIXn75jywc3k6WNYY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;border-bottom: 9px solid rgba(143, 147, 206, 0.26);border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;\">\n     <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: -10px;\">\n      <div style=\"padding-left:13px;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:1.5;padding-right:13px;\">\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">探元计划NextGen AI考古赛道榜单</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;\">(排名不分先后)</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9467040673211781\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1426\" style=\"width: 100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"547\" data-imgfileid=\"503512750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c6d940b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2Fsm1UZBHjpbgPCjSqRmI4S9Y1MJbCfogRQNWosBJWwiaCWCwopPO4RNHdibqfLwSR6YbdMVacKdxazpeB2Wke6XctHwZOc8lmLgpew3U1Dicnn4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"white-space: normal;font-size: 16px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 20px;text-align: center;justify-content: center;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;min-width: 10%;height: auto;box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px;border-bottom: 9px solid rgba(143, 147, 206, 0.26);border-bottom-right-radius: 0px;\">\n     <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"margin-bottom: -10px;\">\n      <div style=\"padding-left:13px;letter-spacing:3px;line-height:1.5;padding-right:13px;\">\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">路演回顾，创新驱动：</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span style=\"letter-spacing: normal;font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">两大赛道终审路演总结</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 16px 8px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在为期两天的路演中，各团队围绕文化场景的真实痛点、创新的技术解决方案与可行的落地规划进行了精彩阐述。项目团队广泛运用生成式AI、分析式AI、多模态大模型、沉浸式三维呈现、情感计算等尖端技术，生动诠释了“数字+文化”所催生的新质生产力，描绘了文化遗产在数字时代焕新的无限可能</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify; margin: 16px 8px 0px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"197\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible !important;width: 29px !important;height: auto !important;\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"20\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"20\" data-fileid=\"503467015\" data-imgfileid=\"503491098\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3e2649d7&a